dct_title_s: Intervalla locorvm Palaestinae digesta per miliaria romana
dct_alternative_sm: Intervalla locorum Palaestinae digesta per miliaria romana
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Bar scale on map given in "Miliarium romanorum".
Shows topography, drainage, distances and travel times between sites, places of historical interest.
Descriptive text throughout and below title.
Decorative title cartouche with illustrations of men and biblical references.
Appears in Reland's Palaestina ex monumentis veteribus illustrata. Utrecht : Willem Broedelet, 1714.
